-->
<command>\setrandom</>を組み込み関数で置き換えました。
(Fabien Coelho)
       </para>

       <para>
<!--
        The new built-in functions include <link
        linkend="pgbench-functions"><function>random()</></>,
        <function>random_exponential()</>, and
        <function>random_gaussian()</>, which perform the same work as
